ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of WILLIAM ARTHUR RESTALL of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Michael D. Campbell, effective September 29, 2014.
